title: Mega Deal Chatter, Toaster Classic
itunes:title: Mega Deal Chatter, Toaster Classic
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – break down the potential deal that could make Andrew Luck the highest paid player in league history & Von Miller turning down the Broncos offer.  Plus, the heroes discuss Cam Newton ending the “dab.”  Then the heroes are joined by NFL Media’s Dave Dameshek for another installment of “Win Wess’ toaster!”
